{"id":"48ce7add-2540-4b38-b4e2-304a352b0f7c","name":"Beast Tamer RPG","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(92, 152, 76);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.47); color: inherit;\">\"People are born surrounded by spirits, beasts that are used in daily life. It might sound cliche to you, as if we live in some type of 'anime' or 'manga', but it's the reality we live in.\"</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>This is my bot that I used all my imagination for. If I were to visualize how I came up with this idea in the first place, it would be...</p><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 0, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(57, 37, 74); color: inherit;\">\"Domain Expansion\"</mark></em></strong></span></h1><h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://c.tenor.com/MuMLDWrW95gAAAAd/tenor.gif?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(100, 0, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(57, 37, 74); color: inherit;\">\"Infinite Creativity\"</mark></em></strong></span></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">... Or just a few manhuas, and/or brainrot clouding my imagination to this 'simple' level.</mark></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(58, 0, 255, 0.52); color: inherit;\">Update V1.1 - </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(58, 0, 255, 0.52); color: inherit;\">Uprising</mark></strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 255);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(58, 0, 255, 0.52); color: inherit;\">- Added </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(58, 0, 255, 0.52); color: inherit;\">Beast Spaces</mark></strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 146, 255);\"><mark